<para_1><b>Issuance of New Shares in <?= data.company.name ?> (the "Company")</b></para_1>
<para_1>Notice is hereby given to all members of the Company that the Directors intend to issue and allot <?= data.number_of_shares ?> <?= data.security_type ?>, at a price of <?= data.price_per_share ?> per share.</para_1>
<? if (data.explanation) { ?><para_1><?= data.explanation ?></para_1><? } ?>
<para_1>As a member of the Company, you possess the right under Articles <?= data.article_for_preemptive_rights ?> of the Company's Articles of Association to participate in this issue of shares.
Given that the Company is issuing <?= data.total_new_shares_on_offer ?> new <?= data.security_type_short ?>, and you presently hold <?= data.shareholder.num_shares ?> out of an existing <?= data.total_existing_securities_in_class ?>, you have the right to subscribe for <?= data.shareholder.pro_rata ?>% of this new issue: <?= (data.shareholder.pro_rata / 100 * asNum_(data.total_new_securities_on_offer)).toFixed(2) ?>
 shares for <?= asCurrency_(currencyFor_(data.price_per_share), (data.shareholder.pro_rata / 100 * asNum_(data.total_round_size)).toFixed(2)) ?>.
You may also have excess rights to subscribe beyond that amount -- if other shareholders do not take up their pro rata allotments, you may partcipate beyond yours, up to the total amount of <?= data.total_round_size ?>.
If you wish to participate in this issue, please indicate, in the attached Issuance Offer Acceptance Notice, the level of your interest.
If you do not participate, <?= commaAnd(data.parties.new_investor, "name") ?>
 <?= plural_verb(data.parties.new_investor, "has") ?>
 indicated the intent to subscribe for new shares not taken up by existing shareholders, up to the total amount on offer.
If we do not hear from you within <?= data.preemptive_rights_notice_period ?> days from the date of this letter, we will understand that you do not wish to participate.</para_1>
<? data.signature_comment = "Director" ?>
